related_questions.question: Do I qualify for Utah unemployment?
related_questions.snippet: Eligibility for Unemployment in Utah. ... You must be unemployed through no fault of your own, as defined by Utah law. You must have earned at least a minimum amount in wages before you were unemployed. You must be able and available to work, and you must be actively seeking employment.
